<span class="displaytext">little rock, ar -- former arkansas governor and presidential candidate (candidate full) has issued the following comment in response to a washington times article reporting he would amend the constitution in connection to children born in the u.s. to illegal aliens: <p>"i do not support an amendment to the constitution that would prevent children born in the u.s. to illegal aliens from automatically becoming american citizens. i have no intention of supporting a constitutional amendment to deny birthright citizenship."</p></span>



